blog.name: reputationproceedsthis
blog.title: Hello!❤️
blog.description:
Mackenzie // 17 // Taylor fan for over a decade and totally her curly hair twin (if I say so myself) //

💕But Darling, it’s going to be okay 💕

body:
TS7 Theory - Blue

Alright, so I basically got tumblr again because I wanted to see and fangirl over everyone’s TS7 theories - and - I have one to contribute and it may be a bit bad but oh well here’s to trying.

  • Alright so theres a lot of rainbow imagery in music video for Me!, obviously, but one color that stuck out to me particularly was the amount of blue (particularly Taylor’s hair at the end w/ the highlights but I’ll get back to that later
  • That instantly rang a bell in my head and reminded me of a lyric from Reputation, the song in particular being Delicate
  • but the lines were “Dark jeans and your Nikes look at you/Oh damn, never seen that color blue”
  • and obviously we know it’s about Joe bc the song is freaking precious
  • then you think about it more
  • and there’s the line in Gorgeous
  • “Ocean blue eyes looking in mine/I feel like I might sink and drown and die”
  • and it’s another blue reference, again talking about Joe, right?
  • So (and I’m going to kind of look at this like a literary analysis alright because I’m a dork) it’s pretty much established that the color blue is established symbolism for Joe, in a way
  • And obviously I don’t know if this would come across more in lyrics or in a song title or something but part of me wonders if the blue hair and the blue imagery in Me! has anything to do with a song that’s going to again be associating blue and Joe
